#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.select_dtypes.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.select\\_dtypes"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.select_dtypes.select_dtypes:1 of
msgid "Return a subset of the DataFrame's columns based on the column dtypes."
msgstr "根据列的数据类型返回 DataFrame 列的一个子集。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.select_dtypes.select_dtypes of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.select_dtypes.select_dtypes:3
#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.select_dtypes.select_dtypes:6 of
msgid ""
"A selection of dtypes or strings to be included/excluded. At least one of"
" these parameters must be supplied."
msgstr "要包含/排除的数据类型或字符串的选择。至少需要提供其中一个参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.select_dtypes.select_dtypes of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.select_dtypes.select_dtypes:10 of
msgid ""
"The subset of the frame including the dtypes in ``include`` and excluding"
" the dtypes in ``exclude``."
msgstr "包含 ``include`` 中的数据类型并排除 ``exclude`` 中的数据类型的帧的子集。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.select_dtypes.select_dtypes of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.select_dtypes.select_dtypes of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.select_dtypes.select_dtypes:14 of
msgid ""
"* If both of ``include`` and ``exclude`` are empty     * If ``include`` "
"and ``exclude`` have overlapping elements     * If any kind of string "
"dtype is passed in."
msgstr ""
"* 如果 ``include`` 和 ``exclude`` 都为空\n"
"    * 如果 ``include`` 和 ``exclude`` 有重叠元素\n"
"    * 如果传入了任何形式的字符串数据类型"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.select_dtypes.select_dtypes:14 of
msgid ""
"If both of ``include`` and ``exclude`` are empty     * If ``include`` and"
" ``exclude`` have overlapping elements     * If any kind of string dtype "
"is passed in."
msgstr ""
"如果 ``include`` 和 ``exclude`` 都为空\n"
"    * 如果 ``include`` 和 ``exclude`` 有重叠元素\n"
"    * 如果传入了任何形式的字符串数据类型"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.select_dtypes.select_dtypes:18 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.dtypes`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.select_dtypes.select_dtypes:19 of
msgid "Return Series with the data type of each column."
msgstr "返回每个列数据类型的 Series。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.select_dtypes.select_dtypes:22 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.select_dtypes.select_dtypes:23 of
msgid "To select all *numeric* types, use ``np.number`` or ``'number'``"
msgstr "要选择所有 *数值* 类型，请使用 ``np.number`` 或 ``'number'``"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.select_dtypes.select_dtypes:24 of
msgid ""
"To select strings you must use the ``object`` dtype, but note that this "
"will return *all* object dtype columns"
msgstr ""
"要选择字符串，您必须使用 ``object`` 数据类型，但请注意这将返回 *所有* "
"对象数据类型列"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.select_dtypes.select_dtypes:26 of
msgid ""
"See the `numpy dtype hierarchy "
"<https://numpy.org/doc/stable/reference/arrays.scalars.html>`__"
msgstr ""
"参见 `numpy 数据类型层次结构 <https://numpy.org/doc/stable/reference/"
"arrays.scalars.html>`__"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.select_dtypes.select_dtypes:28 of
msgid ""
"To select datetimes, use ``np.datetime64``, ``'datetime'`` or "
"``'datetime64'``"
msgstr ""
"要选择日期时间，请使用 ``np.datetime64``、``'datetime'`` 或 ``'datetime64"
"'``"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.select_dtypes.select_dtypes:30 of
msgid ""
"To select timedeltas, use ``np.timedelta64``, ``'timedelta'`` or "
"``'timedelta64'``"
msgstr ""
"要选择时间差，请使用 ``np.timedelta64``、``'timedelta'`` 或 ``'"
"timedelta64'``"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.select_dtypes.select_dtypes:32 of
msgid "To select Pandas categorical dtypes, use ``'category'``"
msgstr "要选择 Pandas 分类数据类型，请使用 ``'category'``"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.select_dtypes.select_dtypes:33 of
msgid ""
"To select Pandas datetimetz dtypes, use ``'datetimetz'`` (new in 0.20.0) "
"or ``'datetime64[ns, tz]'``"
msgstr ""
"要选择 Pandas 带时区的日期时间数据类型，请使用 ``'datetimetz'``（0.20.0 "
"新增）或 ``'datetime64[ns, tz]'``"

